{"tid":966292,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實好多野都好似有個最佳食用日期咁","createTime":"2019-01-02T16:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T21:39:49.000Z","uid":207336,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9a0b762d756fe56f3cbb899d3812384082bbdb78","tid":966292,"uid":207336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:26:32.000Z","msg":"過左個個期限，就食唔到最正既味道<br />\n<br />\n好似表白咁，有時人地對你有好感你唔出擊 到遲啲你走去表白，人地已經過左最鐘意你既時侯<br />\n<br />\n又好似道歉咁，拖得愈耐，件事可能由期待某方開口，到心灰意冷<br />\n<br />\n又好似追夢咁，有刻熱血上腦冇好好食住勢直衝，過左一排熱誠又可能減左dd<br />\n<br />\n所以，有咩諗到有咩想做有咩想講就真係要坐而起行，唔係話過左個timing就做唔到，只係會錯失左你更好既結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d6bfa26d455380cf167ffa4ae2846ac7674cb9","tid":966292,"uid":6783,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:28:09.000Z","msg":"火雞的味道<br />\n最高峰既一瞬間就係未食同第一啖之間"},{"pid":"20e03a9da3e73e057d7f05420e9827fe217329e4","tid":966292,"uid":35538,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:28:47.000Z","msg":"重慶森林？"},{"pid":"fb10dfa3362715d4825cd9dc0cd10aeac0a230ff","tid":966292,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:30:06.000Z","msg":"樓主啱啱收完卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3606cf2c097f43323435cebcc5fd3e35b5bac6b","tid":966292,"uid":207336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb10dfa3362715d4825cd9dc0cd10aeac0a230ff","tid":966292,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:30:06.000Z","msg":"樓主啱啱收完卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:39:50.000Z","msg":"冇 想9up下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf9000bf4788106a7d54371282b161d902ff9c3","tid":966292,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:41:16.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時開始每樣野都有個限期<br />\n曾經有一份真摯既愛情擺係我面前"},{"pid":"6e63c20dc66817140a507eaf5585a